  "title": "*NEW* Assistant Contract Manager (Hospitals) ($5,000 to $5,500) #NJA",
  "description": "<p><strong>The Job: </strong><br /></p><ul><li>Responsible for carrying out day-to-day management and service of the client according to contractual agreement and ensure that quality service is provided cost-effectively to meet the evolving needs of the business</li><li>Provide contract/ operation/ service leadership and participates in developing and implementing consistent policies, procedures, controls in contract execution</li><li>Maintain service level agreements and key performance indicators for services, review regularly in the light of changing business and operational needs</li><li>Meet contractual manpower needs and standards – ensure proper induction program  in place, skills upgrading, career development and retention</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements: </strong></p><ul><li>Degree or Diploma in Management or relevant professional qualification or closely related field with minimum 2 or more years of progressive management\nexperience working in a hospital environment services industry.</li><li>Able to excel in a dynamic and demanding hospital environment while effectively\nleading, organizing, and managing people for facility services projects</li></ul><p><strong>Interested applicants can send their detailed resumes to </strong><a href=\"mailto:janelui@recruitexpress.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">janelui@recruitexpress.com.sg </a><strong>or call JANE @ 6735 1955. </strong></p><p><strong>JANE LUI JIE'EN </strong></p><p><strong>CEI: R1104482</strong></p><p><u><strong>Company Reg. No. 199601303W || EA Licence No. 99C4599</strong></u></p>",
